<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>经管会报告整理工具</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/echarts@5.5.1/dist/echarts.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/xlsx@0.18.5/dist/xlsx.full.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f0f2f5;
      --card: #fff;
      --primary: #1a4a8c;
      --accent: #03a9f4;
      --border: #e4e7ed;
      --text: #303133;
      --muted: #909399;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4a8c 0%, #2d6cb5 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(26, 74, 140, 0.25);
    }
    header h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; }
    header p { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.85; margin-top: 4px; }
    .container { max-width: 1440px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .toolbar {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    }
    .toolbar label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin-right: 4px; }
    .btn {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: opacity .15s;
    }
    .btn:hover { opacity: .88; }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #eef2f7; color: var(--text); }
    .btn-accent { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    input[type="file"] { display: none; }
    .file-label {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      background: #eef2f7;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .file-label:hover { background: #e2e8f0; }
    select {
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .panel {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .panel-head {
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .table-wrap {
      overflow: auto;
      max-height: 420px;
    }
    table.data-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 12px;
      min-width: 1200px;
    }
    table.data-table th,
    table.data-table td {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 4px 6px;
      text-align: right;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    table.data-table th {
      background: #f5f7fa;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    table.data-table th.col-month,
    table.data-table td.col-month {
      text-align: center;
      position: sticky;
      left: 36px;
      background: #fff;
      z-index: 2;
      box-shadow: 2px 0 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
    }
    table.data-table th.col-month { background: #f5f7fa; z-index: 3; }
    table.data-table th.col-ops,
    table.data-table td.col-ops {
      position: sticky;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 4;
      box-shadow: 2px 0 4px rgba(0,0,0,.04);
    }
    table.data-table input {
      width: 72px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      padding: 2px 4px;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: right;
      background: transparent;
    }
    table.data-table input:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      outline: none;
      background: #f0f9ff;
    }
    table.data-table .col-month input { width: 84px; text-align: center; }
    table.data-table input.cell-calc {
      background: #f0f9eb;
      color: #606266;
      cursor: default;
    }
    table.data-table input.cell-calc:focus {
      border-color: transparent;
      background: #f0f9eb;
    }
    table.data-table .col-ops {
      width: 36px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2px;
      background: #fafbfc;
    }
    table.data-table th.col-ops { background: #f5f7fa; z-index: 4; }
    table.data-table .col-ops input[type="checkbox"] { cursor: pointer; }
    .btn-icon {
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1;
      padding: 2px 4px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .btn-icon:hover { background: #fee; color: #f56c6c; }
    .btn-icon-add:hover { background: #e8f5e9; color: #67c23a; }
    th.th-metric { position: relative; }
    th.th-metric .btn-del-col {
      position: absolute;
      right: 2px;
      top: 2px;
      font-size: 11px;
      padding: 0 4px;
      line-height: 16px;
    }
    .table-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .table-actions .sep {
      width: 1px;
      height: 20px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 0 4px;
    }
    .btn-danger { background: #fef0f0; color: #f56c6c; }
    .btn-danger:hover { background: #fde2e2; }
    .charts-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(640px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .chart-card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .chart-card-head {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .chart-box { width: 100%; height: 380px; }
    .empty-hint {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 48px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .status { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-left: auto; }
    @media print {
      header, .toolbar, .panel, .chart-card-head .btn { display: none !important; }
      .charts-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .chart-box { height: 360px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>经管会报告整理工具</h1>
    <p>录入各指标分月数据，一键生成双轴柱状+折线图（样式对齐经管会标准图表）</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="toolbar">
      <label for="excelFile" class="file-label">导入 Excel (.xlsx)</label>
      <input type="file" id="excelFile" accept=".xlsx,.xls" />
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btnLoadSample">加载示例数据</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" id="btnGenerate">生成图表</button>
      <button class="btn btn-accent" id="btnExportAll">导出全部 PNG</button>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="window.print()">打印报告</button>
      <label style="margin-left:8px">展示指标：</label>
      <select id="metricFilter">
        <option value="all">全部 9 项</option>
      </select>
      <span class="status" id="statusText">就绪</span>
    </div>

    <section class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <span>数据录入表 <small style="font-weight:400;color:var(--muted)">（填写去年/当年后自动算环比、同比，浅绿列为只读）</small></span>
        <div class="table-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btnAddRow" type="button">+ 增行</button>
          <button class="btn btn-danger" id="btnDelRows" type="button">− 删选中行</button>
          <span class="sep"></span>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="btnAddMetric" type="button">+ 增指标列</button>
          <select id="delMetricSelect" title="选择要删除的指标"></select>
          <button class="btn btn-danger" id="btnDelMetric" type="button">− 删指标列</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table class="data-table" id="dataTable"></table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="chartsSection">
      <div class="empty-hint" id="emptyHint">录入数据后点击「生成图表」</div>
      <div class="charts-grid" id="chartsGrid" style="display:none"></div>
    </section>
  </div>

